flowchart LR

    User[External User or Service] -->|HTTPS| AFD[Azure Front Door]

    AFD -->|Private Link| VNet[Azure Virtual Network]

    VNet --> AKS[AKS Hosted Application]

    AKS --> Data[Azure Data Services<br/>PostgreSQL and Storage Account]
    AKS --> Secrets[Azure Key Vault]

    AKS --> S3[AWS S3 Outbound Only via Firewall]

    AKS --> APIGW[AWS API Gateway via Firewall<br/>Authenticated using Cognito]
